WEBVTT

51:34.563 --> 51:35.397
Well, I take it back.

51:36.022 --> 51:36.063
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

51:36.105 --> 51:39.397
(dramatic music)

51:40.730 --> 51:41.647
Want me to show you how to do this?

51:42.022 --> 51:43.313
I would suggest you give it a shot.

51:43.855 --> 51:45.438
I see the worst in everyone, Cal.

51:46.522 --> 51:47.147
It's my gift.

51:48.230 --> 51:49.397
And it's the key to my work.

51:50.230 --> 51:53.522
I can see a person's worst
qualities just by looking at him.

51:54.022 --> 51:54.813
See, look at this guy.

51:55.147 --> 51:56.605
He's married, but not to her.

51:56.980 --> 51:58.230
That's why he has a tan line

51:58.230 --> 51:59.397
where his wedding ring should be.

52:00.230 --> 52:01.938
This guy's about to school with that guy.

52:02.730 --> 52:04.438
(laughing) That's
why he's laughing too loud.
